/*
 * Walk model:
 *   start at #TAG
 *   children of node
 *   if child is tag (content starts with #) -> recurse
 *   else -> completion candidate token
 * Cache layers: cvm_children (_ch.bin), content blobs (cache/*.bin),
 * and a local flattened index cache/tag_completion.bin for keystroke path.
